prompts.frontCover: A charming cartoon-style watercolor illustration of a scruffy terrier dog, mid-air, leaping joyfully towards a giant, delicious-looking birthday cupcake that is just out of reach. The dog has a determined, comically wide-eyed expression, with its tongue out and ears flopping. The cupcake is elaborately decorated with colorful sprinkles and a single lit candle. The scene is set against a soft, light-colored background with organic paint bleeds and visible paper texture. Splatters of watercolor paint in bright, happy colors surround the leaping dog, adding to the sense of chaotic celebration. In the center of the design, elegant, readable, handwritten cursive script floats above the cupcake, spelling out the words "happy birthday". The entire image is a flat 2D artwork, capturing the spontaneous and messy joy of a dog's love for treats, rendered with soft, flowing watercolor brush strokes.
